        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html> <html> <head> <meta charset=\"UTF-8\"> <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"> <title>Order Confirmation</title>  <style> body{ margin:0; padding:0; background:#f4f6f8; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; }  .wrapper{ width:100%; background:#f4f6f8; padding:20px 0; }  .container{ max-width:600px; margin:auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }  .header{ background:#2563eb; color:#ffffff; padding:20px; text-align:center; }  .header h1{ margin:0; font-size:22px; }  .content{ padding:25px; color:#333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; }  .order-box{ background:#f9fafb; padding:18px; border-radius:6px; margin-top:15px; }  .order-box p{ margin:6px 0; }  .product-table{ width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin-top:10px; }  .product-table th{ text-align:left; padding:8px; background:#f1f5f9; font-size:14px; }  .product-table td{ padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-size:14px; }  .footer{ background:#f1f5f9; padding:18px; text-align:center; font-size:13px; color:#666; }  @media screen and (max-width:600px){  .content{ padding:18px; font-size:14px; }  .header h1{ font-size:20px; }  } </style> </head>  <body>  <div class=\"wrapper\"> <div class=\"container\">  <div class=\"header\"> <h1>Scriptly Store</h1> </div>  <div class=\"content\">  <p>Hello <strong>{{ $json['Customer Name'] }}</strong>,</p>  <p>🎉 Thank you for your order! Your purchase has been successfully confirmed.</p>  <div class=\"order-box\">  <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{ $json['Order Id'] }}</p> <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{OrderDate}}</p>  <table class=\"product-table\">  <tr> <th>Products Ordered</th> </tr>  <tr> <td>{{ $json.Prdoucts }}</td> </tr>  </table>  </div>  <p>If you have any questions about your order, feel free to reply to this email.</p>  <p>We appreciate your business and hope you enjoy your purchase!</p>  </div>  <div class=\"footer\"> <p>© 2026 Scriptly Store</p> <p>Thank you for shopping with us.</p> </div>  </div> </div>  </body> </html>",
